welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Port Orchard, the charming city known for its picturesque waterfront, vibrant local culture, and breathtaking views. We're excited for you to explore and experience all that our city has to offer. Enjoy your stay!"

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Industrial Airport handles all domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Cargo Terminal
terminals.description: The cargo terminal at Industrial Airport is used for shipping and receiving freight.

wifi.note: Free wifi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport, also known as Sea-Tac Airport, houses the majority of the airport's services and amenities.

terminals.name: North Satellite Terminal
terminals.description: The North Satellite Terminal at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport is primarily used for Alaska Airlines flights.

terminals.name: South Satellite Terminal
terminals.description: The South Satellite Terminal at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport is primarily used for international flights.

wifi.note: Free Wi-Fi is available throughout the airport. Simply connect to the network and accept the terms and conditions to access.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at McChord AFB Airport serves both civilian and military flights.

terminals.name: Military Terminal
terminals.description: The military terminal at McChord AFB Airport is exclusively for military personnel and their families.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Sanderson Field Airport serves all commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: General Aviation Terminal
terminals.description: This terminal is dedicated to private and charter flights at Sanderson Field Airport.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.
